Luminora solar farm - Global Energy Monitor - GEM.wiki\\\",\\\"content\\\":\\\"Luminora solar farm (Planta solar fotovoltaica Luminora Solar) is a solar photovoltaic (PV) farm in pre-construction in Murcia, Region of Murcia, Spain.\\\",\\\"score\\\":0.6680367,\\\"raw_content\\\":null},{\\\"url\\\":\\\"https://newsroom.ferrovial.com/en/press-releases/ferrovial-to-build-three-photovoltaic-plants-in-murcia-spain-with-capacity-to-supply-30500-homes/\\\",\\\"title\\\":\\\"Ferrovial to build three photovoltaic plants in Murcia, Spain, with ...\\\",\\\"content\\\":\\\"Ferrovial will build three new photovoltaic plants for TotalEnergies and Soltec in Spain's Murcia region. The plants will have a total capacity of 116 MWp.\\\",\\\"score\\\":0.6512002,\\\"raw_content\\\":null}],\\\"response_time\\\":1.64,\\\"request_id\\\":\\\"ccc2a48e-eef9-4e36-a203-deefe28c0ea9\\\"}]\"],\"options\":{\"api_key\":{\"lc\":1,\"type\":\"secret\",\"id\":[\"GROQ_API_KEY\"]},\"model\":\"moonshotai/kimi-k2-instruct-0905\",\"temperature\":0.7},\"response\":{\"response\":{\"generations\":[[{\"text\":\"\",\"generationInfo\":{\"finish_reason\":\"tool_calls\"}}]]},\"tokenUsage\":{\"completionTokens\":51,\"promptTokens\":1522,\"totalTokens\":1573}}}"}}
