event, focused on advancing U.S. solar and energy storage markets. RWE is expanding its battery storage business with an innovative technology for grid stability.\\\",\\\"score\\\":0.3085344,\\\"raw_content\\\":null},{\\\"url\\\":\\\"https://www.bnamericas.com/en/news/chile-us2bn-clean-energy-projects-submitted-for-environmental-review\\\",\\\"title\\\":\\\"Chile US$2bn clean energy projects submitted...\\\",\\\"content\\\":\\\"Chile US$2bn clean energy projects submitted for environmental review - BNamericas Image 1: Logo BNamericas *    Industries  Industries Electric PowerMining & MetalsOil & GasInfrastructureWater & WastePetrochemicalsICTFinancial Services  *   Companies Image 6: Chile Chile US$2bn clean energy projects submitted for environmental review Image 7: Projects Image 8: Contacts Image 9: Companies 83,000+**key contacts** related to companies and projects Image 10: News *     United States+1 *     Congo (Republic) (Congo-Brazzaville)+242 *     Guinea (Guinée)+224 *     Papua New Guinea+675 *     Saint Barthélemy+590 *     Saint Helena+290 *     Saint Lucia+1 *     Saint Martin (Saint-Martin (partie française))+590 *     South Korea (대한민국)+82 *     South Sudan (‫جنوب السودان‬‎)+211 *     United Arab Emirates (‫الإمارات العربية المتحدة‬‎)+971 *     United Kingdom+44 Company Name*   Image 11: BNamericas #### Products *   Companies #### Industries\\\",\\\"score\\\":0.16840546,\\\"raw_content\\\":null}],\\\"response_time\\\":2.58,\\\"request_id\\\":\\\"ee3ad830-6583-401f-8c45-021d050735ba\\\"}]\"],\"options\":{\"api_key\":{\"lc\":1,\"type\":\"secret\",\"id\":[\"GROQ_API_KEY\"]},\"model\":\"openai/gpt-oss-120b\",\"temperature\":0.7},\"response\":{\"response\":{\"generations\":[[{\"text\":\"\",\"generationInfo\":{\"finish_reason\":\"tool_calls\"}}]]},\"tokenUsage\":{\"completionTokens\":145,\"promptTokens\":2388,\"totalTokens\":2533}}}"}}
