s, bonds, equity investments, financial close announcements (amount, lender/investor, status).\\n* **Notable contractors**: EPC, turbine supplier, or technology provider if named.\\n* **Source details**: title, publisher, URL, publication date.\\n* **Confidence level**: how strong the evidence is (official vs media vs rumor).\\nHuman: Chile\\nAI: \\nTool: [{\\\"query\\\":\\\"Chile solar farm construction start 2026 permit\\\",\\\"follow_up_questions\\\":null,\\\"answer\\\":\\\"Chile's construction of a solar farm is set to start in April 2026. The project is part of a USD-500m initiative. It will enter commercial operation by 2028.\\\",\\\"images\\\":[],\\\"results\\\":[{\\\"url\\\":\\\"https://renewablesnow.com/news/chiles-colbun-starts-permitting-for-usd-500m-solar-bess-project-1268796/\\\",\\\"title\\\":\\\"Chile's Colbun starts permitting for USD-500m solar, BESS ...\\\",\\\"content\\\":\\\"Chile's Colbun starts permitting for USD-500m solar, BESS project ... Construction is planned to commence in April 2026, according to the plan.\\\",\\\"score\\\":0.8790744,\\\"raw_content\\\":null},{\\\"url\\\":\\\"https://list.solar/news/colbun-initiates/\\\",\\\"title\\\":\\\"Colbun Initiates $500M Solar and Storage Project in Chile\\\",\\\"content\\\":\\\"Construction Start Date: Scheduled to commence in April 2026. Operational Timeline: Expected to start operations in 2028, aligning with Chile's\\\",\\\"score\\\":0.8655088,\\\"raw_content\\\":null},{\\\"url\\\":\\\"https://www.power-technology.com/data-insights/power-plant-profile-gabriela-solar-pv-park-chile/\\\",\\\"title\\\":\\\"Power plant profile: Gabriela Solar PV Park, Chile\\\",\\\"content\\\":\\\"The project construction is expected to commence from 2026. Subsequent to that it will enter into commercial operation by 2027. For more\\\",\\\"score\\\":0.82694983,\\\"raw_content\\\":null},{\\\"url\\\":\\\"https://www.ess-news.com/2025/10/03/chiles-900-mwh-kronos-storage-project-enters-environmental-assessment/\\\",\\